      areaSpecificH2: 'Why Mayfair trust reviews are the highest-value planning conversation available',
      areaSpecificParagraph: 'A Mayfair trust structure set up fifteen years ago may no longer qualify for the tax treatment assumed at the time, and a review that identifies this can save hundreds of thousands or millions in eventual tax, depending on the estate size. Specialist trust advisors handle this kind of engagement routinely in W1, and the cost of the review is usually trivial relative to the consequences of leaving the structure unreviewed.',
